data.description: WELCOME to your NEW HOME located at 4338 Schooner Ln. It has a big canal access from the back.    This home has a fantastic contemporary floor plan with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, a remodeled open kitchen, granite and sterling steel appliances, adjacent to a very large Florida room, large living room with a fireplace for those romantic nights...Windows, roof and many of the rooms have been redone after the hurricane Michael.  It has a separate Dining room. The bathrooms are large and in good condition.  The backyard is huge with over half an acre fenced in for privacy with a new deck.  Landscaped with automatic sprinkler system.  The LOAN is calling for a qualified ASSUMABLE BUYER!!!!  THIS HOME IS READY FOR SOMEONE TO CALL IT THEIR HOME...HOME IS IN EXCELLENT LOCATION CLOSE TO SHOPPING, SCHOOLS, AND HOSPITALS.  Seller willing to buy down interest rate with a right offer!
